  `mutating_actions: []`, `phase2_execution_actions: []`, `overall_score`,
  `readiness_status`, and per-prerequisite scores.
- Standard run artifacts written under `.promptclaw/runs/<run-id>/`:
  `outputs/phase2-readiness.json`, `routing/route.json`, `routing/route.md`,
  `handoffs/phase2-readiness.md`, `summary/final-summary.md`,
