docs/coherence-foundations.md:205:    role: str            # lead, verify, or empty
docs/coherence-foundations.md:252:This block is injected into the agent's prompt via the `coherence_context` parameter in `build_lead_prompt()` and `build_verify_prompt()`.
docs/coherence-foundations.md:266:    applies_to: [lead, verify]
docs/coherence-foundations.md:297:Trust updates happen in the `_update_trust()` method of `CoherenceEngine`, called by hooks B, D, and F (post-routing, post-lead, post-verify).
docs/coherence-foundations.md:329:| E    | `pre_verify`   | Before verification        | Inject decisions + rules into verifier   |
docs/coherence-foundations.md:330:| F    | `post_verify`  | After verification verdict | Evaluate verdict, update trust           |
