## Correctness

The implementation matches the spec precisely.

- `run_pal_phase2_readiness_report(...)` is present in `pal_agent.py` and runs
  five fixed read-only tools in order (`pal_health`, `pal_smoke_baseline`,
  `shutdown_remote_audit`, `phase2_project_state`, `vast_boundary`).
- Six prerequisites are scored:
  `operator_authorization` (always `blocked`, score `0.0`),
  `phase1_health_baseline`, `shutdown_safety`, `deployment_reproducibility`,
  `cost_and_vast_boundary`, and `phase2_execution_boundary`.
- Payload records `workflow_id: phase2_readiness_report`,
